---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bleap Review 2026: Zero FX Fees Crypto Card | GetNoKYC">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> → 
      <a href="/reviews/" class="hover:text-white">Reviews</a> → Bleap
    </nav>

    <header class="mb-12">
      <span class="badge badge-verified mb-4">VERIFIED</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Bleap Review 2026: Zero FX, Non-Custodial</h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <span class="text-yellow-500">★★★★½ 4.4/5</span>
        <span class="text-gray-400">EU Only</span>
        <span class="text-emerald-500">Non-Custodial</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Network</span><p class="font-medium">Mastercard</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">FX Fee</span><p class="font-medium text-emerald-500">0%</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Cashback</span><p class="font-medium">2% USDC</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">ATM</span><p class="font-medium text-emerald-500">Free</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Custody</span><p class="font-medium">Non-custodial</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Crypto</span><p class="font-medium">BTC, ETH, SOL</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>What is Bleap?</h2>
      <p>Bleap is a <strong>non-custodial Mastercard</strong> with zero FX fees and 2% USDC cashback. Perfect for EU travelers tired of hidden currency conversion charges.</p>

      <h2>Pros</h2>
      <ul class="text-emerald-400">
        <li>✅ <strong>Zero FX Markup</strong> — Spend abroad without fees</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>2% USDC Cashback</strong> — Paid in crypto</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Free ATM</strong> — Cash withdrawals included</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Non-Custodial</strong> — You control keys</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cons</h2>
      <ul class="text-red-400">
        <li>❌ <strong>EU Only</strong> — Limited availability</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Newer Platform</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p><strong>Best for EU travelers.</strong> Zero FX + free ATM = huge savings if you spend in multiple currencies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="https://bleap.finance" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-cta">Get Bleap →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
      <a href="/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline">← Back to all cards</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
<style>.prose h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: white; } .prose p { color: #d1d5db; margin-bottom: 1rem; } .prose ul { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }</style>
